title: Amy Landecker and the Critical Reception of 'Transparent' (Ep. 190)
description:
The Ringer’s Andy Greenwald sits down with actor Amy Landecker to discuss her pathway into comedic roles, awards season, and the critical reception she’s received for her work on ‘Transparent.’
